personalInfo.clubAffl: Rockliffe Hall GC (County Durham, United Kingdom)

tourBios.intlVics: (3): 2004 Attjari Wafa-Tikida Beach Moroccan Classic [EurChal], Ryder Cup Wales Classic [EurChal]. 2007 French Open [Eur].
tourBios.curYearHigh: Shot four rounds in the 60s at the Omega European Masters (64-66-64-68) and finished regulation at Crans-sur-Sierre GC tied with David Lipsky. In the sudden-death playoff, made a bogey to Lipsky's par to finish solo second.
tourBios.carHigh: 2007: Came from five strokes back entering the final round in early July to win the French Open on the European Tour. It was his first European Tour title.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA TOUR was T6th in 2008 at the World Golf Championships-CA Championship.
